Class GlobalDfsAI

  • java.lang.Object
    • AI.AI
      • AI.GlobalAI
        • AI.GlobalDfsAI

  • public class GlobalDfsAI
extends GlobalAI
    AI agent that uses a DFS search approach, looking at the entire known map to make the safest moves. Identical to GlobalAI, except uses a stack instead of queue for picking unvisited nodes, which leads to less backtracking
